textBeforeTable: Premier Graduates With names such as Black Caviar, Sacred Kingdom, Weekend Hussler, Starspangledbanner and South Africa’s Igugu synonymous with the Inglis Melbourne Premier Yearling Sale, no buyer can afford not to be there at Inglis Premier in 2012. The 2012 Inglis Melbourne Premier Yearling Sale will be held at Oaklands over four days from February 27 to March 1. Inglis Melbourne Premier Yearling Sale graduates have won 45 Group One races around the globe in the last five seasons. Sale Overview 615 - 790 1st Mar 2012 --> Pedigree
